Package org.bremersee.geojson

This package contains classes for reading and writing GeoJSON with the Jackson JSON Processor.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractGeoJsonCrs
    Abstract base class for the coordinate reference system (CRS) of a GeoJSON object (see http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#coordinate-reference-system-objects ).
    GeoJsonFeature
    A GeoJSON object with the type Feature (see http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#feature-objects ).
    GeoJsonFeatureCollection
    A GeoJSON object with the type FeatureCollection is a feature collection object (see http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#feature-collection-objects ).
    GeoJsonLinkedCrs
    A link to the coordinate reference system (CRS) of a GeoJSON object (see http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#linked-crs ).
    GeoJsonNamedCrs
    A reference to the coordinate reference system (CRS) of a GeoJSON object by it's name (see http://geojson.org/geojson-spec.html#named-crs ).
    GeoJsonObjectMapperModule
    A Jackson JSON processor module that provides the processing (serialization and deserialization) of the following types: Geometry Point LineString Polygon MultiPoint MultiLineString MultiPolygon GeometryCollection
    GeometryDeserializer
    A Jackson deserializer for a Geometry.
    GeometrySerializer
    A Jackson serializer for a Geometry.
    GeometryWrapper
    This class wraps a geometry and can be processed by the Jackson JSON processor without registering the GeoJsonObjectMapperModule.
    GeometryWrapper.Deserializer
    Deserializer for the GeoJSON geometry wrapper class.
    GeometryWrapper.Serializer
    Serializer for the GeoJSON geometry wrapper class.

Package org.bremersee.geojson Description

This package contains classes for reading and writing GeoJSON with the Jackson JSON Processor.
